5 (b) Instead of meeting the requirements in subsection (a) of this section, any applicant
6 who is licensed as a cosmetologist, hair designer, esthetician, natural hair care specialist, or
7 manicurist in another state shall be admitted to practice in this State under the same reciprocity
8 or comity provisions that the state in which the applicant is licensed grants to persons licensed in
9 this State.
10 (c) The Board may establish standards for issuing a license to an applicant who is licensed
